</p><p>Levezonet eo bet Latvia, e-hed hecâh istor, gant ar broioÃ¹ nes, <a href="/wiki/Alamagn" title="Alamagn">Alamagn</a>, <a href="/wiki/Polonia" title="Polonia">Polonia</a>, <a href="/wiki/Sveden" title="Sveden">Sveden</a> ha <a href="/wiki/Rusia" title="Rusia">Rusia</a>.
